body:
@Alonski @andytudhope This is a really good idea. 

We already agreed in the team that translations are more data than code so at some point we would move it to edn or json files, which would make things even simpler. 

I had this idea of a web UI or a special mode in the app to change translations but we really don't have the time in the core team to work on that kind of side tracks. So if you want to create an issue and work on it it is more than welcomed.
